oai_dc:dc.dc:title: An unusual cyclopentaannulation reaction: Thermolysis of an alpha,beta-unsaturated Fischer carbene complex anchored on a Fe-2(CO)(6)(mu-Se)(2) core
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: MATHUR, P
GHOSH, S

insertion
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An unusual annulation of-a Fischer carbene complex anchored on a Fe-2(CO)(6)(mu-Se)(2) core is examined. Thermolysis of Fe-2(CO)(6){mu-SeC(Ph)=C(Se)[(OEt)C=Cr(CO)(5)]} in THF yields an unusual annulated product, [Fe-2(CO)(6)Se-2{mu-(CO)(3)Cr(eta(5)-C5H(CH2Ph)(Ph)(OEt))}] (1), as characterized by IR and H-1, C-13, and Se-77 NMR spectroscopies, and its structure has been established by single-crystal X-ray diffraction.
